00:32:19.335 --> 00:32:20.755
If they were able to simply indicate

766
00:32:20.755 --> 00:32:22.035
that they supported a bill or didn't,

767
00:32:22.035 --> 00:32:24.035
and we were able to provide that data to committees,

768
00:32:24.615 --> 00:32:25.835
um, that could be useful.

769
00:32:25.835 --> 00:32:27.395
Neither of these things are scientific.

770
00:32:27.395 --> 00:32:28.715
Neither the number of submissions

